    "## 11. GPU显存计算方法\n",
    "\n",
    "### 显存组成\n",
    "\n",
    "推理时GPU显存主要由以下部分组成：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{Total Memory} = \\text{Model Params} + \\text{KV Cache} + \\text{Activations} + \\text{Overhead}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. 模型参数显存\n",
    "\n",
    "| 精度 | 每参数字节数 | 7B模型 | 13B模型 | 70B模型 |\n",
    "|------|-------------|--------|---------|----------|\n",
    "| FP32 | 4 bytes | 28 GB | 52 GB | 280 GB |\n",
    "| FP16/BF16 | 2 bytes | 14 GB | 26 GB | 140 GB |\n",
    "| INT8 | 1 byte | 7 GB | 13 GB | 70 GB |\n",
    "| INT4 | 0.5 bytes | 3.5 GB | 6.5 GB | 35 GB |\n",
    "\n",
    "公式:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{Model Memory} = N_{\\text{params}} \\times \\text{bytes\_per\_param}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. KV Cache显存\n",
    "\n",
    "Transformer自回归生成时需要缓存历史的Key和Value：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{KV Cache} = 2 \\times n_{\\text{layers}} \\times n_{\\text{heads}} \\times d_{\\text{head}} \\times \\text{seq\_len} \\times \\text{batch} \\times \\text{bytes}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中系数2来自K和V各一份。\n",
    "\n",
    "| 模型 | 层数 | heads | d_head | seq=2048, bs=1, FP16 |\n",
    "|------|------|-------|--------|----------------------|\n",
    "| 7B (LLaMA) | 32 | 32 | 128 | 1.0 GB |\n",
    "| 13B | 40 | 40 | 128 | 1.6 GB |\n",
    "| 70B | 80 | 64 | 128 | 4.2 GB |\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. 激活值显存\n",
    "\n",
    "推理时的中间激活值（比训练时小很多）：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{Activations} \\approx 2 \\times n_{\\text{layers}} \\times d_{\\text{model}} \\times \\text{seq\_len} \\times \\text{batch} \\times \\text{bytes}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 4. 实用经验公式\n",
    "\n",
    "**FP16推理（无量化）:**\n",
    "$$\\text{Memory} \\approx 2 \\times N_{\\text{params}} \\text{ (bytes)} + \\text{KV Cache}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**INT4量化推理:**\n",
    "$$\\text{Memory} \\approx 0.5 \\times N_{\\text{params}} \\text{ (bytes)} + 0.5 \\times \\text{KV Cache}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "注意：量化后KV Cache通常仍用FP16存储。"
   ]
  },
